---
import BaseHead from '../../../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../../../components/Header.astro';
import TopStrip from '../../../../components/TopStrip.astro';
import Footer from '../../../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <BaseHead title="申請撤銷通報 — Go Bali Go" description="" noSuffix />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
</head>
<body>
  <Header lang="blog" />
  <TopStrip lang="zh-tw" />

  <main class="redact-page">
    <div class="redact-container">
      <a href="/forum/account/" class="back-link">← 返回帳號</a>
      <h1 class="redact-title">申請撤銷通報</h1>

      <div class="redact-card">
        <h2>如何申請撤銷？</h2>
        <p>如果你希望刪除或修改你曾發布的通報，請透過以下方式聯絡我們：</p>
        <ol class="redact-steps">
          <li>寄送電子郵件至 <a href="mailto:admin@gobaligo.id" class="email-link">admin@gobaligo.id</a></li>
          <li>主旨請填寫：<strong>申請撤銷入境通報</strong></li>
          <li>
            信件內容請包含：
            <ul>
              <li>你的 Google 帳號電子郵件</li>
              <li>通報的入境日期與機場</li>
              <li>申請理由（選填）</li>
            </ul>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="redact-note">我們將在 3 個工作天內處理你的申請。審核通過後，通報將從公開列表中移除。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="redact-info">
        <h3>關於隱私保護</h3>
        <p>你的通報不會包含可直接識別身份的個人資料（如姓名、護照號碼）。若通報中含有你認為需要保護的內容，請透過上述方式聯絡我們。</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</body>
</html>

<style>
.redact-page { padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem; }
.redact-container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }

.back-link { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--ocean); text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; margin-bottom: .8rem; }
.back-link:hover { color: var(--gold); }
.redact-title { font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--ocean); margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }

.redact-card {
  background: #fafaf8;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,.2);
  border-radius: 12px;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
}
.redact-card h2 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ocean); margin: 0 0 .8rem; }
.redact-card p { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--text); margin: 0 0 .8rem; }
.redact-steps { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--text); padding-left: 1.4rem; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 .8rem; }
.redact-steps ul { margin: .3rem 0; padding-left: 1.2rem; }
.email-link { color: var(--ocean); font-weight: 600; }
.redact-note { font-size: .82rem; color: var(--text-light); margin: 0; }

.redact-info {
  background: #eff6ff;
  border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
  border-radius: 10px;
  padding: 1.1rem 1.3rem;
}
.redact-info h3 { font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1d4ed8; margin: 0 0 .5rem; }
.redact-info p { font-size: .85rem; color: #1e3a5f; margin: 0; }
</style>
